": "January 11, 1987", "format": false, "excerpt": "Days after Hank Ballard's passing, Bruces Springsteen and Hornsby (along with former Steel Mill bandmate Robbin Thompson) pay tribute by playing Ballard's last great hit.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Cover Me&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Cover Me", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/cover-me/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/admin-ajax-100.jpg?fit=500%2C500&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200}, "classes": []}, {"id": 33904, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1988/08/12/matr-bruce-springsteen-and-the-swingin-medallions-double-shot-of-my-babys-love/", "url_meta": {"origin": 8423, "position": 5}, "title": "Double Shot (Of My Baby&#8217;s Love)", "author": "Ken", "date": "August 12, 1988", "format": false, "excerpt": "One time only: The E Street Band teams up with beach music legends The Swingin' Medallions to cover one of rock's enduring party classics.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Cover Me&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Cover Me", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/cover-me/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/doubleshot.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/doubleshot.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/doubleshot.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/doubleshot.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/doubleshot.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}], "_links": {"self": [{"href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/8423", "targetHints"